# Optional: point the operator console at the local situational-agent HTTP server.
# Unset by default — the app then runs off the baked fixture with zero network calls.
# Set this (copy to app/.env) once the agent server is up to run Ask/Override/advisory live against local Gemma.
# Routes and shapes: contracts/agent_http.md
# VITE_AGENT_URL=http://localhost:8000
